CARD MEMBERS MOST RECENT CREDIT INFORMATION AND SPEND PATTERNS. ADDITIONALLY, GLOBAL SPEND LIMITS ARE ESTABLISHED TO LIMIT THE MAXIMUM EXPOSURE FOR THE COMPANY.

