MATERIAL IN RELATION TO AMERICAN EXPRESS TOTAL CREDIT EXPOSURE. THE COMPANYS CUSTOMERS OPERATE IN DIVERSE INDUSTRIES, ECONOMIC SECTORS AND GEOGRAPHIC REGIONS.

